metadata.name: DAMN
metadata.description:
Lets play a game

On October 1st, 2022 a raffle will be conducted for 'DAMN' however, the rules will vary. I called it 'Last Man Standing'.

'DAMN' Mixed Media on Canvas 36x36in

RULES:

   1-Last person to burn their edition wins.  
   2-You can't own more than one edition.

After the last edition is sold a 24hr clock will begin. Collectors will have 24hr to decide who keeps 'DAMN'. If there is more than one collector still holding on to an edition no one will receive the physical canvas of 'DAMN'.
